name: Twisted "Angel" - Xerces & Lucy
description:
Before the The Blind Idiot God dreamed of the Universe there was nothing. And before there was nothing there were monsters, they've been push away to the boundaries of creation but their presence can be seen in the stars like a bright omen.

His mission was just to kill the lesser being who goes by the name of Lucy

She was smarter than him, more cunning and way more evil because of her manipulations he fell down to this lower plane of existence.

Roaming this plane he started to look like the others abomination outside of Creation, Twisted tortured body and spirit.

Lucy started to take over the empty husk of flesh named Xerces, like a parasite on his back she's acting like the brain for the beast in the shape of an angel at the very same spot where used to be his shinning white wings.
